# Normalize all text files to LF in the repo and on checkout. LF works for
# PowerShell 5.1+, bash, and shellcheck alike, so we keep a single line ending
# everywhere and avoid CRLF/LF churn across platforms.
*           text=auto eol=lf

# Be explicit that shell scripts must always be LF (bash/shellcheck break on CRLF).
*.sh        text eol=lf
